  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/9b093a2b84a4d7869c9d52fcf2fe2d88.poster.avif?t=1732806671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/9b093a2b84a4d7869c9d52fcf2fe2d88.webm?t=1732806671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/9b093a2b84a4d7869c9d52fcf2fe2d88.mp4?t=1732806671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help Luna in saving her forest from the evil forces, who occupied Luna's forest and started calling the forest as their own.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> Tons of collectables to collect to proceed to the next part of the world.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> More enemies to fight and defeat including some bosses<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/6d6bd793205ba05d7a30f122442c0bf3.avif?t=1732806671\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras_big/6d6bd793205ba05d7a30f122442c0bf3.avif?t=1732806671 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> Plenty of hurdles to overcome.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/00cc89c894e6aa186ea9fc9ae315583e.avif?t=1732806671\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras_big/00cc89c894e6aa186ea9fc9ae315583e.avif?t=1732806671 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> Huge worlds to explore in this thrilling story driven classic 3d Platformer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/91af0e40e4f5b1031e7436e5e03d0eca.poster.avif?t=1732806671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/91af0e40e4f5b1031e7436e5e03d0eca.webm?t=1732806671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601660/extras/91af0e40e4f5b1031e7436e5e03d0eca.mp4?t=1732806671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
